fees.description: For information on additional fees, a full schedule of charges is available from http://www.momentumenergy.com.au/fees
A 0.53% fee (GST Incl) will apply to payments made by any credit or debit card.

electricityContract.terms: Time of use charges are based on Australian Eastern Standard Time, except when daylight savings applies in which case interval meters are adjusted to Australian Eastern Daylight Time, unless indicated otherwise. Full terms and conditions can be obtained from www.momentumenergy.com.au/terms-and-conditions or by contacting our Customer Care Team on 1800 SWITCH.
electricityContract.variation: We will give you written notice of any variations to your rates & charges under your terms and conditions in accordance with applicable legal requirements.

incentives.eligibility: A one-off $50 (GST incl) sign-up credit will be applied to your first electricity bill. This credit cannot be redeemed for cash or transferred to another supply address.

eligibility.information: This plan is only available to residential customers who sign up a new supply address, agree to direct debit, eCommunications and eBilling and have the necessary metering system configuration.

greenPowerCharges.description: For an added 4.95 c/kWh incl. GST, you can purchase GreenPower for either 10, 20, 25, 50, 75 or 100% of your usage.

electricityContract.onExpiryDescription: The agreement continues until terminated by you or us in accordance with your terms and conditions.
